            <h1 id="page-title">Alert (TA14-212A)</h1>
            <h2 id="page-sub-title">Backoff Point-of-Sale Malware</h2>
            <div class="submitted meta-text">
                                Original release date: July 31, 2014  | Last <a href="#revisions">revised</a>: September 30, 2016
                                            </div>
